  <TITLE>Setting to make VAT number required or optional</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>Let's add this setting to require VAT numbers to be entered. It could be very useful for B2B shops. Add this setting to Admin area &gt; Tax settings page &gt; VAT block. It'll be a new child &quot;'VAT number' required&quot; setting displayed below the &quot;EU VAT enabled&quot; (when enabled). This setting will be disabled by deault. And it'll be used on the registation and &quot;customer info&quot; pages Forum topics: - https://www.nopcommerce.com/en/boards/topic/99613/make-vatnumber-mandatory-from-plugin - https://www.nopcommerce.com/en/boards/topic/54032/suggestion-make-vat-field-per-checkbox-as-a-required-field - https://www.nopcommerce.com/en/boards/topic/13117/vat-on-registration</DESCRIPTION>
